trans-unit.source: Represents the binding element for the named pipe transport.
trans-unit.target: Representerer bindingselementet for den navngitte datakanalen transporten.

trans-unit.source: This transport uses URIs of the form "`net.pipe`://`hostname`/`path`".
trans-unit.target: Denne transport bruker URIer på formen "`net.pipe`://`hostname`/`path`".

trans-unit.source: Other URI components are optional.
trans-unit.target: Andre URI-komponenter er valgfrie.

trans-unit.source: The NamedPipeTransportBindingElement class is the starting point for creating a custom binding that implements the named pipes transport protocol.
trans-unit.target: Klassen NamedPipeTransportBindingElement er utgangspunkt for å opprette en egendefinert binding som implementerer transportprotokollen for navngitte datakanaler.

trans-unit.source: This transport is used for on-machine [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]-to-[!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] communication.
trans-unit.target: Denne transport brukes for på maskinen [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]- til -[!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] kommunikasjon.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service model uses this class to create factory objects that implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interfaces.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service modellen bruker denne klassen for å opprette fabrikk objekter som implementerer den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory>og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener>grensesnitt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory>

trans-unit.source: These factory objects then create and accept the channels that transmit SOAP messages using the named pipes protocol.
trans-unit.target: Objektene fabrikken Opprett og godta kanaler som overfører SOAP-meldinger ved hjelp av navngitte datakanaler-protokollen.

trans-unit.source: You configure the factories that this class creates by setting its properties, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement.ConnectionPoolSettings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan konfigurere fabrikker som denne klassen oppretter ved å angi egenskapene, for eksempel: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement.ConnectionPoolSettings%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement.ConnectionPoolSettings%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also set properties on the base class, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.TransferMode%2A>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.ConnectionBufferSize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan også angi egenskaper i basisklassen, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, eksempel: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.TransferMode%2A>, og <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.ConnectionBufferSize%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.ConnectionBufferSize%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.TransferMode%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: For a complete list of properties, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: En fullstendig liste over egenskaper, kan du se <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: Finally, you can set properties on the base class of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, which is <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>, such as <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Til slutt kan du angi egenskaper på basisklassen av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, som <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>, for eksempel <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>

trans-unit.source: For a complete list of properties, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: En fullstendig liste over egenskaper, kan du se <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>
